          "reviewTitle": "Great for mature skin!",
          "reviewText": "Feels very light and doesn't settle in pores or lines. I'm 55 so I would know. I purchased Ivory and Buff. The ivory is a bit too pink and I'm more neutral. The buff is a true neutral. It's not orangy or too yellow or too pink. I kept both. I could mix them if I want and that looks good too. Not a lot of coverage but I don't mind. The finish is nice. It's not too matte and it's not sparkly or too luminous. I'm pretty fair/light and the shades are pretty forgiving if you choose the wrong one. Looks good all day and doesn't oxidize. Great price for this product.I would purchase again.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on February 16, 2026",
          "customer": "momof4",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AEQHIN4UOEYUXIMZTXP4ERNEEDRQ",
